nodes.text: Lanoree Brock's mother was a female Human Je'daii Master who served as instructor at Bodhi, the Temple of Arts, for the Je'daii Order on Tython at the height of the Infinite Empire's reign. Brock and her husband were the parents of Lanoree Brock, a Je'daii Ranger, and Dalien Brock the founder of the Stargazers.
